title: SiblingRange (FunctionBlock)
text:
FUNCTION_BLOCK FINAL SiblingRange IMPLEMENTS
IModuleRangeForward
The range of all siblings of a module instance.  The order is
as defined by the module tree. The range starts with a given
module instance.
